## Step \#5: Email\! 

Send the prospectus/sponsorship package for the 2nd email\! REPLY QUICKLY. DO NOT leave them for more than three hours, reply WITHIN THE DAY.  

Don‚Äôt overwhelm them with information. Try to jump on a call or meet them in person to explain everything. Emails are easy to refuse, but a puppy-eyed teen? Not as much.  

